{"tid":2111971,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何柱國沽星島股權套2.25億","createTime":"2020-07-17T03:04:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T06:41:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ffcafaf904b7d614730df724763309a7dd7432","tid":2111971,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200717/RFXCXQPFQS2S3BLTTX5GETFYVQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200717%2FRFXCXQPFQS2S3BLTTX5GETFYVQ%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFacF7E3yEolOTrLLafiBe6Y0%3D&h=3db873c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200717%2FRFXCXQPFQS2S3BLTTX5GETFYVQ%2F&h=74912796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200717/RFXCXQPFQS2S3BLTTX5GETFYVQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n何柱國沽星島股權套2.25億<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O4X3L08cdJ5g3LHdst5elrlA5is=/640x426/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NOBLJERZ6QW3DLQTZVKEPUGSEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO4X3L08cdJ5g3LHdst5elrlA5is%3D%2F640x426%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNOBLJERZ6QW3DLQTZVKEPUGSEU.jpg&h=362aeb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星島主席何柱國。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】主要經營報章《星島日報》的星島（1105）宣佈，主席何柱國旗下Luckman Trading Limited，已與一間獨立配售代理完成配售協議，並以每股1.5元出售1.5億股或17.07%股權予若干獨立投資者，套現2.25億元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n月底或公佈賣盤結果<br />\n<br />\n完成後，何柱國持股減少至約2.76億股或31.43%。不過，何柱國透過Luckman Trading仍為星島之控股股東，但多項資料顯示，賣盤一事已開始明朗化。<br />\n<br />\n星島去年。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據中央結算紀錄，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n星島昨早市。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"9776e772ffeec0879bfd5f4d918e396931e46e12","tid":2111971,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:06:18.000Z","msg":"仲套現到, 算勁！"},{"pid":"c18f08ff4f561951daa5bfc7f1a9a0444ea661ef","tid":2111971,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:21:12.000Z","msg":"套埋都係得幾億。"},{"pid":"c3fd5e7b14f0776c4e4d05523bddada5c2cb1d7c","tid":2111971,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"不要讓親共美國人何柱國跑了"},{"pid":"53f036eef5463921626f10e253cb72d22780b922","tid":2111971,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:46:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3a75a6d43e823a3bbb1cd6f1715fff1ee8cad5c","tid":2111971,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T03:48:48.000Z","msg":"想走？<br />\n邊度對得住黨？"},{"pid":"e2b81d1b23db3a9613d0336c9907828be9a8df8b","tid":2111971,"uid":291803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"走資派 人人喊打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對得住國家咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96351ddbb6c0b3f67c025c7afac66a9d0ee861ab","tid":2111971,"uid":161711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:09:16.000Z","msg":"星島紅報"},{"pid":"e897b6d6c7945d652e3ddf76c9455504d04f9728","tid":2111971,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"識 play wor"},{"pid":"ae9f20523e7bcf7264ad9160af52aed9d0093e2b","tid":2111971,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e897b6d6c7945d652e3ddf76c9455504d04f9728","tid":2111971,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"識 play wor"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T05:34:47.000Z","msg":"Yep!!!!!<br />\nCash is KIN